Sentencas: A co-tape casting technique was applied to fabricate electrolyte/anode for solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Microstructure and electrochemical characterization of solid oxide fuel cells fabricated by co-tape casting

Sentencas: YSZ and NiO-YSZ powders are raw materials for electrolyte and anode, respectively.
Titulo: Microstructure and electrochemical characterization of solid oxide fuel cells fabricated by co-tape casting

Sentencas: Through adjusting the Polyvinyl Butyral (PVB) amount in Slurry, the co-sintering temperature for electrolyte/anode could be dropped.
Titulo: Microstructure and electrochemical characterization of solid oxide fuel cells fabricated by co-tape casting

Sentencas: After being co-sintered at 1400 C for 5 h, the half-cells with dense electrolytes and large three phase boundaries were obtained.
Titulo: Microstructure and electrochemical characterization of solid oxide fuel cells fabricated by co-tape casting

Sentencas: The improved unit cell exhibited a maximum power density of 589 mWcm(-2) at 800 C. At the voltage of 0.7 V, the current densities of the cell reached 667 mAcm(-2).
Titulo: Microstructure and electrochemical characterization of solid oxide fuel cells fabricated by co-tape casting

Sentencas: When the electrolyte and the anode were cast within one step and sintered together at 1250 C for 5 h and the thickness of electrolyte was controlled exactly at 20 mu m, the open-circuit voltage (OCV) of the cell could reach 1.11 V at 800 C and the maximum power densities were 739, 950 and 1222 mWcm(-2) at 750, 800 and 850 C, respectively, with H-2 as the fuel under a How rate of 50 sccm and the cathode exposed to the stationary air.
Titulo: Microstructure and electrochemical characterization of solid oxide fuel cells fabricated by co-tape casting

Sentencas: Under the voltage of 0.7 V, the current densities of cell were 875, 1126 and 1501 mAcm(-2), respectively.
Titulo: Microstructure and electrochemical characterization of solid oxide fuel cells fabricated by co-tape casting

Sentencas: These are attributed to the large anode three phase boundaries and uniform electrolyte obtained Under the lower sintering temperature.
Titulo: Microstructure and electrochemical characterization of solid oxide fuel cells fabricated by co-tape casting

Sentencas: The electrochemical characteristics of the cells were investigated and discussed.
Titulo: Microstructure and electrochemical characterization of solid oxide fuel cells fabricated by co-tape casting
